  "remarks": "\nGolden Sun Sky Entertainment Co., Ltd. is an involved person under the Global Human Rights Sanctions Regulations 2020 because it is responsible for, has facilitated, and has concealed evidence of, activity that violates the right not to be subjected to torture or cruel, inhuman or degrading treatment or punishment or the right not to be required to perform forced or compulsory labour.   \n",
